Part 5 — Implement Unit Tests (AAA Pattern)
Task 5.1 — ConvertCToF Tests

Implement all of the following:

    Two [Fact] tests:
        0°C → 32°F
        –1°C → 30.2°F
    One [Theory] test with at least 5 [InlineData] cases.

Use NullLogger so tests do not write real logs:

// Using NullLogger so the test does not write actual log output.
var logger = NullLogger<WeatherForecastController>.Instance;

