    Add a comment where you removed direct instantiation (new) to explain why DI is preferred.
    Comment any usage of wrapper dependencies to explain how they enable deterministic tests.

8.2 — Required Comments in Wrapper Classes

    Explain why the wrapper exists (e.g., abstracting DateTime.Now or Random for predictable testing).

8.3 — Required Comments in Program.cs

